  ---
  To build and run the server, from the repository root:

  go run ./srv/cmd/spacegame

  or build a binary first:

  go build -o spacegame ./srv/cmd/spacegame
  ./spacegame

  The server reads nearest.csv and planets.csv from the working directory, so you must run it from
   the repository root (where those files live). It listens on http://127.0.0.1:8080.

  The placeholder web/dist/index.html is served at / until you build the frontend. When that's
  ready, run cd web && npm run build and rebuild the binary to embed the compiled SPA.

